quran[182]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,"Mi woo…óndirii cappniraa…ói …óin saffaaji."
  37,2,"Mi woo…óndirii coggiray…ói (duule) …óin coggugol."
  37,3,"Mi woo…óndirii janngirat…ói …óin, ganndintinorgol:"
  37,4,"""Pellet, dewetee…óo mon on, ko bajjo,"
  37,5,"Jey…óo kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde …óin …ói…ói, Jey…óo kadi pu…óir…óe …óen."
  37,6,"Min cu…óirii kammu (hikkii ngu) aduna ngun: cu…óaari koode …óeen,"
  37,7,"e deenirgol (ngu) kala seytaane da…óaandu."
  37,8,"∆äi ka…ótanaaka ke…óitagol mbatu [Maleykaaji toowu ngu ngun; tawde hi…ói peroree e kala baŇčŇče,"
  37,9,"ka fa…óagol (…ói). Hino woodani …ói kadi, lepte duumii…óe."
  37,10,"Si wonaa ndun bifti ndu e majji, jilannde [haala], ndu rewnree hoodere tufatnde."
  37,11,"La…ďndo …ďe: si ko kam…ďe …ďuri sa…ótude takde kaa ko …ďen …ďe Min tagi? Min tagirii …ďe kam…ďe, loopal narnungal."
  37,12,"Si ko woni, a haawi, he…ďe njalnora!"
  37,13,"Si …ďe mbaajaama, …ďe mbajitortaa;"
  37,14,"si …ďe nji'ii ma'ande, …ďe njalkita,"
  37,15,"…ďe mbii'a: ""∆äuum wonaani, si wonaa mbilewu …ďanngu ngu."
  37,16,"Eyoo si min maayii, min ngontii mbullaari e ∆īi'e, haray ko min immintinoytee…ďe?"""
  37,17,"Baabiraa…ďe amin adinoo…ďe …ďeen kadi e minen?"""
  37,18,"Maaku: ""pellet! Hara le ko on hoynaa…ďe""."
  37,19,"Nganndon …óum, ko wuttaandu wo'oturu pet, tawee jaka yoo, he…ďe ndaara,"
  37,20,"∆Āe mbi'a: Ee bone amen ! Ko ndee woni √Ďaaande njo…ďdi kuu…óe""."
  37,21,"""Ko ndee woni √Ďalaande √Īaawoore, ko njeddatno…óon fii mum""."
  37,22,"Moo…ďee too√Ī…ďe …ďen, e nandadii…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, e kon ko …ďe ngonnoo e rewde,"
  37,23,"ko woori Alla. Coggiree…ďe ka laawol Jahiimi."
  37,24,"Ndarnon …ďe, tawde ko …ďe la…ďnditetee…ďe""."
  37,25,"""Ko he…ďi on, on mballindirtaa?"""
  37,26,"Ko woni kam…ďe …ďe hannde, ko …ďe jebbilii …ďe,"
  37,27,"wo…ó…ďe e ma…ď…ďe peewtita …ďeya, …ďe la…ďndondira;"
  37,28,"…ďe mbi'a: ""Ko onon ngoni ko ardiranaynoo men, ka …ďaŇčŇče √Īaamo""."
  37,29,"(Koohoo…ďe) …ďen mbi'a: ""Ko woni kon, on mee…óaano won'de gooŇč…óin…ďe."
  37,30,"Doole woo min ngalanaano on. Si ko woni, on ngonno yim…ďe bew…ďe."
  37,31,"Konngol Joomi men ngol, jojjii e min; pellet, ko en mee…óoo…ďe [lepte …óen]."
  37,32,"Min mbewinno on, tawde hay minen, ko min bewnoo…ďe""."
  37,33,"Kam…ďe on nden √Īande, ko …ďe haawtoytee…ďe ka lepte."
  37,34,"Ko nii Minen Min ngollirtata bom…ďe …ďen."
  37,35,"Kam…ďe si …ďe mbi'anooma: ""dewetee…óo alaa si wonaa Alla"", …ďe mawnintinoo."
  37,36,"…ďe mbi'a: ""Kere men ngaccitiray dewetee…ói amen …óin, fii yimoowo kaangaa…óo?"""
  37,37,"Si ko woni, (Nulaa…óo) on ko goonga ardi, o goongini nulaa…ďe …ďen."
  37,38,"Pellet, ko on mee…óay …ďe lepte mu'usuu…óe …óen."
  37,39,"On njo…ďetetaake, si wonaa yeru kon ko ngollatno…óon."
  37,40,"si wonaa jiyaa…ďe Alla la…ď…ďinaa…ďe …ďen,"
  37,41,"hino woodani …ďen …óoon, fanndaare ganndaandi:"
  37,42,"muuyantee…ói, kadi ko …ďe teddintee…ďe,"
  37,43,"ka aljannaaji neeminii…ói,"
  37,44,"e hoore dan…óe, ko …ďe feewtondir…ďe."
  37,45,"Hara kore he…óe mbannginii e ma…ď…ďe, immorde e …ďulirde"
  37,46,"daneeje, lew√Īunde, fii yaroo…ďe,"
  37,47,"mu'usuu…óe hoore alaa e majjam, wonaa …óam ciwrinirtee…ďe …óam."
  37,48,"Hino woodani …ďe (toon): ra…ď…ďu…ďe ndaar…óe, yaaja gitee…ďe,"
  37,49,"wa'a…ďe wa …ďoccoo…óe maraa…óe."
  37,50,"Wo…ó…ďe e ma…ď…ďe peewtita …ďeya, …ďe la…ďndondira."
  37,51,"Go…ó…óo e ma…ď…ďe wi'a: ""Min mi…óo marunoo gonndiijo,"
  37,52,"wi'atnoo…óo: ""Kere ko a jiyaa…óo e gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen?"
  37,53,"Eyoo si en maayii, en wontii mbullaari e ∆īi'e, tawa ko en yo…ďitoytee…ďe?"""
  37,54,"O wi'a: ""Taw si …óon nji…ói ∆īeewde?"""
  37,55,"O ∆īeewa, o haynoo oya ka leri dulbunge,"
  37,56,"o wi'a: ""Mi woo…óndirii Alla ! A …óe…ď…ďi fii no mi halkorde!"
  37,57,"Si wonaano mo∆ī∆īere Joomi am nden, mi tawdeteno e [leptetee…ďe …ďeen]."
  37,58,"Wonaa noon en maayataa,"
  37,59,"si wonaa maayde men aranere nden, en wngonaani kadi leptetee…ďe?"""
  37,60,"Pellet, ko …óuum …óoo woni maloore mawnude ndeen."
  37,61,"Ko fii sugu …óuum …óoo, woni yo golloo…ďe ngollan."
  37,62,"Hara ko …óuum …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude jipporde, kaa ko leggal ""Zaqquumi"" [ngal kaa…óugal]?"
  37,63,"Min mba…óii ngal jarrabuyee too√Ī…ďe …ďen."
  37,64,"Ngal, ko leggal jaltatngal ka tummbere Dulbunge."
  37,65,"Dim…óe maggal, hono wa'i no ko'e seytanooji."
  37,66,"Kam…ďe …ďe, pellet, ko e maggal …ďe √Īaamirta, …ďe kebbinira ngal deedi ma…ď…ďe."
  37,67,"Refti hino woodani …ďe e dow maggal, njaram patinaa…óam."
  37,68,"Refti ruttorde ma…ď…ďe ndeen, ko ka Dul…ďoowe."
  37,69,"∆Āe tawu baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďeen, ko majjunoo…ďe,"
  37,70,"…ďe ngoni e yaccagol njokka ba…óteeji ma…ď…ďe."
  37,71,"GooŇč…óii, ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e adam…ďe …ďen, majjiino, ado ma…ď…ďe."
  37,72,"GooŇč…óii le, Min nuluno e ma…ď…ďe, jeertinoo…ďe."
  37,73,"Kono ndaaru ba…ótane …ďren jeertinanoo…ďe, no wa'anoo!"
  37,74,"Si wonaa jiyaa…ďe Alla, la…ď…ďinaa…ďe …ďen."
  37,75,"GooŇč…óii Nuuhu nodduno Min, Min mo∆ī∆īii jaabotoo…ďe."
  37,76,"Min nda…óni mo, kaŇčko e yim…ďe makko …ďeen, e suno mawnngo ngon,"
  37,77,"Min mb…ói gelngol makko ngol, heddotoo…ďe …ďen."
  37,78,"Min ngaccani mo mantoore, e sakkitii…ďe …ďeen."
  37,79,"Kisal wonii e Nuuhu, e ndeer winndere nden."
  37,80,"Ko non woni ko Min mbarjorta mo∆ī∆īim…ďe …ďen."
  37,81,"KaŇčko, ko o jeyanoo…óo e jiyaa…ďe Amen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  37,82,"Refti Min njooli heddii …ďe …ďeen."
  37,83,"Hino jeyanoo e jokkunoo…ďe mo …ďe Ibraahiima."
  37,84,"Tuma nde ardunoo e Joomi makko, e …ďernde hisnde."
  37,85,"Nde o maakannoo ben makko e yim…ďe mum …ďeen: ""Ko hol…óum ndewoton?"
  37,86,"E ko dewetee…ói pefindaa…ói, ko wanaa Alla, paala…óon?"
  37,87,"Ko cikku…óon e Joomiraawo tagoore ngon?"""
  37,88,"O ndaariri ndaarande to koode,"
  37,89,"o maaki: ""Ko mi √Īawn…óo""."
  37,90,"∆Āe ngacci mo, …ďe nduŇčti."
  37,91,"O mooltii e dewetee…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin, o maaki: ""E on √Īaamataa?"
  37,92,"Ko he…ďi on, on kaalataa?"""
  37,93,"O naatnani, fiyirde …ói √Īaamo ngon."
  37,94,"∆Āe peewti e makko, hi…ďe njaawno."
  37,95,"O maaki: ""E on ndeway ko lesu…óon!,ceh…óon)."
  37,96,"hara le ko Alla tagi on, e ko ngolloton?"""
  37,97,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Mahanee mo mahdi, mbugo…óon mo ka dul…ďayange""."
  37,98,"∆Āe pa'andanii mo feere; kono Min mb…ói …ďe sooybe …ďen."
  37,99,"O maaki: ""Min on, ko mi peroowo ka Joomi am, aray nde O feewnata kam."
  37,100,"Joomi am, wee…óam ge…óal mo∆ī∆īu…ďe""."
  37,101,"Min mbeltiniri mo, ge…óal mu√Ī√Īii…óo."
  37,102,"Nde on yottinoo e makko jahal, [Ibraahiima] maaki: ""Ko an …ďi…ó…óo am, min mi yi'ii e …óoyngol, won'de mi…óo hirse. Ndaaru ko yi'i…óaa"". [Ismaa'iila] maaki: ""eey ma baaba'en, mba…óee ko njamira…óon kon, on tawoyay kam, si Alla ja…ďii, jiyaa…óo e mu√Īii…ďe …ďen""."
  37,103,"Nde …ďe jebbilaninoo (yamiroore Alla nden), o hippiri mo tiinde nde,"
  37,104,"Men noddiri mo wi'ide: ""eey ma yo Ibraahiima !"
  37,105,"Pellet, a gooŇč…óiinii koy…óol ngol. Ko Minen Min njo…ďirte mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  37,106,"Pellet, ko …óuum …óoo woni jarrabuyee …ďanngu…óo oon."
  37,107,"Min cootiri mo kirse maw…óe."
  37,108,"Min ngaccani mo mantoore, e sakkitii…ďe …ďen."
  37,109,"""Kisal wonii e Ibraahiima""."
  37,110,"Ko wano nii Min njo…ďirta mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďeen."
  37,111,"KaŇčko, ko o jiyaa…óo e jiyaa…ďe Amen goo…óin…ďe …ďen."
  37,112,"Min mbeltiniri Ishaaqa, Annabaajo jiyaa…óo e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen."
  37,113,"Min kebbini barki e makko e Ishaaqa. Hino e ge√Īngol ma…ď…ďe ngol: mo∆ī∆īin…óo, e too√Īu…óo hoore-mun …ďanngini."
  37,114,"GooŇč…óii Min mo∆ī∆īike e dow Muusaa e Haaruuna,"
  37,115,"Min nda…óni …ďe, kam…ďe e yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďeen, e ngo∆īo mawnungo,"
  37,116,"Min mballi …ďe, …ďe ngoni fool…ďe …ďen."
  37,117,"Min ngokki …ďe deftere …ďannginnde ndeen."
  37,118,"Min peewniri …ďe, e laawol pocciingol ngol."
  37,119,"Min ngaccani …ďe mantoore, e sakkitii…ďe …ďeen."
  37,120,"""Kisal woni e dow Muusaa yo Haaruuna""."
  37,121,"Ko wano nii Min no…ďitirta mo∆ī∆īim…ďe …ďen."
  37,122,"Kam…ďe …ói…óo, ko …ďe jiyanoo…ďe e jiyaa…ďe Amen goo…óiin…ďe …ďen."
  37,123,"Pellet, Ilyaasa kadi, ko jeyanoo…óo e Nulaa…ďe …ďeen."
  37,124,"JaŇčto nde o maakannoo yim…ďe makko …ďen: ""E on kulataa [Alla]?"
  37,125,"E ko ""Ba'ala"" ndewoton, ngaccon …ďur…óo mo∆ī∆īude tagoore nde?"
  37,126,"Woni Alla, Jey…óo on, Jeyi baabiraa…ďe mon adinoo…ďe …ďeen?"""
  37,127,"∆Āe njeddii mo, awa non, ko …ďe tawnoytee…ďe (ka lepte)."
  37,128,"Si wonaa jiyaa…ďe Alla la…ď…ďinaa…ďe …ďeen."
  37,129,"Min ngaccani mo mantoore, e sakkitii…ďe …ďen."
  37,130,"""Kisal woni e dow Ilyaasiina'en""."
  37,131,"Ko wano nii Min njo…ďirta mo∆ī∆īim…ďe …ďeen."
  37,132,"KaŇčko, ko o jeyanoo…óo e jiyaa…ďe Amen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  37,133,"Pellet, Luutu kadi, ko jiyanoo…óo e Nulaa…ďe …ďeen."
  37,134,"JaŇčto nde Min nda…óndunoo mo, kaŇčko e …ďeynguure makko nden fof,"
  37,135,"si wonaa nayeeja debba, tawaa…óo e luttunoo…ďe …ďeen,"
  37,136,"refti Min o∆ī∆īi heddii …ďe …ďeen."
  37,137,"Onon non, ho…óon ndewa e hoore-ma…ď…ďe, dawol mon."
  37,138,"e jemma. E on kaqqiltaa?"
  37,139,"Pellet, Yuunusa kadi, ko jiyanoo…óo e Nulaa…ďe …ďeen."
  37,140,"JaŇčto nde o dogirnoo ka laana hebbinaaka,"
  37,141,"o urbinii, o jiyaa e foolaa…ďe …ďeen."
  37,142,"Liinngii ngii mo…ói mo, ko o pelnii…óo."
  37,143,"Si wonaano tawde homo jeyanoo e subbunhinotoo…ďe …ďen,"
  37,144,"o √Īii…ďayno e reedu maggii, ha √Īalnde ummintinoytee."
  37,145,"Min mberlii mo ka ladde, ko o √Īawn…óo."
  37,146,"Min pu…óini e mayre, leggal buudi."
  37,147,"Min nuli mo e ujune teemeder yim…ďe, maa ko …ďuri."
  37,148,"∆Āe ngooŇč…óini, Min ndakmiti …ďe haa e dumunna."
  37,149,"La…ďndii …ďe:"" E ko Joomi maa woodanta …ďi…ď…ďe rew…ďe, kam…ďe kan wor…ďe?"
  37,150,"Kaa Min tagir Maley'ikaaaji deww…óinaa…ói, hara ko …ďe seedii…ďe?"""
  37,151,"Paamee, kam…ďe e pepindaale ma…ď…ďe …óen, hi…ďe mbi'a:"
  37,152,"""Allah jibinii""; pellet, …ďe penat"
  37,153,"Hara O cu…ďay …ďi…ď…ďe rew…ďe …ďen e dow wor…ďe …ďen?"
  37,154,"Ko he…ďi on, si …óon √Īaawira noon?"
  37,155,"E on miijtottaako?"
  37,156,"Kaa ho…óon njogii hujja …ďanngu…óo?"
  37,157,"Haray ngaddee deftere mon nden, si wonii ko on gooŇč…óu…ďe!""."
  37,158,"∆Āe mba…ói hakkunde makko e Maleykaaji, asko; hara non, Maleykaaji no nganndi, …ďen ko tawnoytee…ďe (ka lepte)."
  37,159,"Senaare woodani Allah, e ko …ďe cifotoo!"
  37,160,"Si wonaa jiyaa…ďe Allah la…ď…ďinaa…ďe …ďen."
  37,161,"Nganndon onon e ko ndewoton kon,"
  37,162,"on ngonaani majjinoo…ďe …óuum [go…ó…óo goo],"
  37,163,"si wonaa taw…óo on ko naatoowo ka Dul…ďaynge."
  37,164,"[Maleykaaji mbi'i'i]: ""Alaa e amen, mo alanaa …óum, daror…óe ganndaande;"
  37,165,"Ko minen ngoni oni saffinaa…ďe …ďeen;"
  37,166,"Ko minen kadi ngoni subbunhinotoo…ďe …ďen."
  37,167,"∆Āe ngoniino e bii'gol:"
  37,168,"""Hara deftere iwnde e adinoo…ďe …ďeen, no woodannoo min,"
  37,169,"min ngonayno jiyaa…ďe Allah la…ď…ďinaa…ďe."
  37,170,"∆Āe njeddi nde, kono aray …ďe nganndoya !"
  37,171,"GooŇč…óii Konngol Amen ardinoke, fii jiyaa…ďe Amen, Nulaa…ďe …ďen,"
  37,172,"won'de pellet, ko kam…ďe ngoni walletee…ďe …ďen,"
  37,173,"e won'de ko konu Amen ngun, woni fooloo…ďe …ďen."
  37,174,"∆äuurno …ďee, ha e saanga;"
  37,175,"ndaaraa …ďe, …ďe aray nji'a!"
  37,176,"E hara ko lepte amen men …óen …ďe ke√Īorta?"
  37,177,"Si …óe njippike ka tannde (dingiral)ma…ď…ďe, haray bimmbi waajonoo…ďe …ďeen bonii !"
  37,178,"∆äuurno …ďee, ha e saanga;"
  37,179,"ndaaraa, …ďe aray nji'a!"
  37,180,"Senaare woodanii Joomi maa, Jey…óo teddungal, e ko …ďe cifotoo !"
  37,181,"Kisal wonii e Nulaa…ďe …ďen,"
  37,182,"Jettooje ngoodani Allah, Jey…óo winndere nden!"
